The latest edition of Because You Said So! took place at the Junction Mall in Nairobi. BYSS is Kenya’s premiere improv comedy show. Founded by Jason Runo, it involves getting a cast of improvisers to make up scenarios, skits and stories on the fly before a live audience. Runo led the cast that included June Gachui and Patricia Kihoro.  Key guests included Nairobi Senator Johnstone Sakaja.      